headline: 3 Beaten-Down Dividend Aristocrats Ready to Rebound by 100%

headline: TransUnion Stock Gains 6% Post Reporting Q3 Earnings & Revenue Beat
summary: TRU lifts its full-year guidance after third-quarter 2025 earnings and revenues beat estimates, driving a 5.8% post-results stock price increase.

headline: UPS Profit, Revenue Fall but Saw Strong International Growth
summary: United Parcel Service logged lower profit and revenue in its third quarter, but sales volume gains across its international segment offset declines in its domestic business.
